{"tid":2360714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★納粹集中營點名制】8℃戶外等8小時，檢測陰性後 院方仍三度拒絕檢測者入室內","createTime":"2021-01-10T04:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T04:30:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74d4271554a8c1bbf54e3fe4ff1bc94e7e4486bf","tid":2360714,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"明報專訊】有公立醫院在嚴寒下要求新冠病毒檢測者在戶外等結果。家人確診的陳小姐本身在酒店檢疫，前日因嘔及頭痛被送往東區醫院，於8℃嚴寒下在室外帳篷等近8小時，雖已穿兩件衫和一件羽絨，並自備暖貼，兼向院方拿了3張氈，但仍「凍到震」。入夜確定檢測陰性後，院方三度拒讓她入室內，至午夜才可入負壓房，最終衛生署專車在翌日凌晨3時許到來接她回酒店，單是等車花了6小時。她斥責院方「好唔人道」，「無病都吹到有病」。港島東醫院聯網總監陸志聰就此致歉，承諾檢討。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20210110/s00002/1610216939393/8℃帳篷等8小時-檢測者轟不人道-穿羽絨披3氈仍「凍到震」-東區醫院認不足\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210110%2Fs00002%2F1610216939393%2F8%E2%84%83%E5%B8%B3%E7%AF%B7%E7%AD%898%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E8%80%85%E8%BD%9F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93-%E7%A9%BF%E7%BE%BD%E7%B5%A8%E6%8A%AB3%E6%B0%88%E4%BB%8D%E3%80%8C%E5%87%8D%E5%88%B0%E9%9C%87%E3%80%8D-%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=2fad8eb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210110%2Fs00002%2F1610216939393%2F8%E2%84%83%E5%B8%B3%E7%AF%B7%E7%AD%898%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E8%80%85%E8%BD%9F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93-%E7%A9%BF%E7%BE%BD%E7%B5%A8%E6%8A%AB3%E6%B0%88%E4%BB%8D%E3%80%8C%E5%87%8D%E5%88%B0%E9%9C%87%E3%80%8D-%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3&h=068af11c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20210110/s00002/1610216939393/8℃帳篷等8小時-檢測者轟不人道-穿羽絨披3氈仍「凍到震」-東區醫院認不足</a>"},{"pid":"788e06252e461cafb004b90afb8da93c6be7e937","tid":2360714,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新納粹"},{"pid":"824a12787b644ec8a4ea7df1581ea60104f8f4d7","tid":2360714,"uid":53062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"算好，集中營要裸體"},{"pid":"f6bc71625657076aa06dc51d51deef960398ba95","tid":2360714,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:53:41.000Z","msg":"match 納粹集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n囚徒在營里有很多日常任務。每天的作息包括：黎明醒來，整理床鋪，早上點名，出營工作，長時間干苦力，為一頓可憐的飯排隊，返回營地，牢房檢查，晚上點名。<span class=\"xx-large\">點名期間，無論天氣如何，衣衫極其單薄的囚徒必須紋絲不動，靜靜站上幾個小時</span>。"},{"pid":"9a54e31817fa3ae36ba6b73eb74e146ceec6e0d8","tid":2360714,"uid":121580,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"凍撚到中普通肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9da4251baec102e64b7c3e8841865a2e0c6b64","tid":2360714,"uid":82628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:56:05.000Z","msg":"檢測帶來自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80956fe10e74e4b1d6645cf6dc89703677784dda","tid":2360714,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"企